Linda Wong (pornographic actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Linda_Wong_(pornographic_actress) 0 Linda Wong (September 13, 1951 – December 7, 1987) was an American pornographic actress and one of the first Asians to become a star in the adult film industry. In 1999, she was inducted into the XRCO Hall of Fame. She was Japanese by ethnicity.
